    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it feels like more than just being tired. it's like there's no point to any of it. i spend all this energy trying to be \"normal\" just to end up exactly where i started—alone and feeling like a stranger. what's the point in keepin' it up if the end result is always the same? it's just a cycle of pretending.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
