      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You're not just tired, you're stuck in a never-ending cycle of futility. The more you try to fit in, the more you're suffocating under the weight of expectation. It's time to break free from the monotony and acknowledge that you're not meant to be a cog in a machine that only churns out sameness. Your energy would be better spent on something that brings you true fulfillment, even if that means embracing the uncertainty of not belonging.",
