      "content": "but there is no way to embrace not belonging and still feel okay. there's no \"fulfillment\" in just being an outcast forever. it just feels like i'm waiting for something that's never gonna happen. sometimes i think the only way to actually stop the noise and the exhaustion is to just... stop being part of it. to just have some actual peace.",
